## ⚙️ **.gitignore**
PaymentGateway
Use this at the root of your repo to exclude Python, cache, environment, and VS Code-specific files:

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.pytest_cache/
*.coverage
.env
.venv/
venv/
env/

# Logs
*.log
*.out

# Byte-compiled
*.egg-info/
build/
dist/

# VS Code
.vscode/
.history/
.settings/

# Docker
*.pid
*.tar
*.log
docker-compose.override.yml

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Kubernetes configs (optional)
*.kubeconfig
